":{"docs":{},"f":{"docs":{},"l":{"docs":{},"o":{"docs":{},"w":{"docs":{"11":{"ref":11,"tf":0.3184713375796179}},"s":{"docs":{"11":{"ref":11,"tf":0.15923566878980894}}}}}}}}}}},"x":{"5":{"5":{"2":{"0":{"2":{"0":{"docs":{"11":{"ref":11,"tf":0.15923566878980894}}},"docs":{}},"docs":{}},"docs":{}},"docs":{}},"docs":{}},"docs":{}}},"length":146},"corpusTokens":["09","1","2022","22t12:16:04+01:00","38.70","45.33","5.79","a","about","actuarial","add","additionalinformation","also","an","and","are","assessment","assessment.scores.ogrs.determined","assessment.scores.rsr.determined","assessmentdate","assessments","been","business","by","can","changes","conducted","context","crn","data","delius","dependencies","description","detailurl","determined","development","domain","event","eventnumber","events","eventtype","example","exist","filter","filtered","following","for","formats","from","generated","get","group","h","have","helps","hmpps","https","identifiers","in","incoming","info","integration","interface","interfaces","is","listens","map","message","messages","might","more","need","not","oasys","occurredat","of","offender","ogrs","on","or","osp","ospcontactband","ospcontactscore","ospindecentband","ospindecentscore","person","personreference","policy","predictor","predictors","probation","provided","queue","rar","recidivism","reconviction","reoffending","responds","risk","rsr","rsrband","rsrscore","rsrstaticordynamic","sample","scale","score","scores","serious","service","sexual","some","source","specific","sqs","static","stored","submitted","system","the","this","to","tree","two","type","types","understand","update","updated","updates","url","used","user","users","v","value","version","via","we","when","where","will","with","within","workflow","workflows","x552020"],"pipeline":["trimmer"]}, "docs": {"11":{"title":"About","content":"Risk Assessment Scores to Delius\nUpdates risk assessment scores in Delius following assessments in the OASys Offender Assessment system.\nThis integration service listens for domain events generated by OASys and updates Delius with changes to the following\nrisk scores:\n\n\nRisk of serious recidivism (RSR)\nOASys sexual reoffending predictor (OSP)\nOffender group reconviction scale (OGRS)\n\nThe scores are updated when an OASys risk assessment is submitted for a Person on Probation.\nBusiness need\nHelps the business users understand the actuarial risk predictors within the Delius user interface.\nData dependencies\nThis integration service is used to update the RSR and OSP risk scores in Delius. The service will also add/update scores from OGRS risk assessments for a Person on Probation and an Event in Delius.\nContext map - Risk Assessment Data\n\nWorkflows\n\n        \n          \nBusiness Event\nMessage Event Type/Filter\n\nRisk scores updated\nrisk-assessment.scores.rsr.determined\n\nRisk assessment\nrisk-assessment.scores.ogrs.determined\n\n        \n      Risk Score Workflow\nTwo types of scores are provided in the risk score data: risk of serious recidivism (RAR) and OASys sexual reoffending predictor (OSP). The scores are updated in Delius.\n\nOGRS Risk Assessment Workflow\nAn OGRS risk assessment is conducted for a Person on Probation for a specific Event. The offender group reconviction scale (OGRS) score is stored or updated in Delius when the risk assessment is submitted.\n\nInterfaces\nMessage Formats\nThe service responds to HMPPS Domain Event messages via the\nRisk Assessment Scores and Delius Queue.\nExample messages are in the development source tree.\nIncoming messages are filtered on eventType by the SQS queue policy\nOASys Domain Event\nSample message:\n{\n  \"eventType\": \"risk-assessment.scores.rsr.determined\",\n  \"version\": 1,\n  \"description\": \"Risk assessment scores have been determined\",\n  \"detailUrl\": \"https://some-url-where-we-can-get-more-info-this-might-not-exist\",\n  \"occurredAt\": \"2022-09-22T12:16:04+01:00\",\n  \"additionalInformation\": {\n    \"RSRScore\": 45.33,\n    \"RSRBand\": \"H\",\n    \"RSRStaticOrDynamic\": \"STATIC\",\n    \"OSPIndecentScore\": 5.79,\n    \"OSPIndecentBand\": \"H\",\n    \"OSPContactScore\": 38.70,\n    \"OSPContactBand\": \"V\",\n    \"EventNumber\": 1,\n    \"AssessmentDate\": \"2022-09-22T12:16:04+01:00\"\n  },\n  \"personReference\": {\n    \"identifiers\": [\n      {\n        \"type\": \"CRN\",\n        \"value\": \"X552020\"\n      }\n    ]\n  }\n}\n","url":"/"}}}